templates.name: Warmaster
templates.description: The ultimate master of warfare, capable of coordinating strategic actions on a planetary scale. Commands with unmatched vision and expertise.

templates.name: Supremacy Warden
templates.description: A battle-hardened leader, master of navigating perilous situations. Known for turning the tide in desperate engagements.

templates.name: Overlord
templates.description: A true warlord capable of leading and coordinating large groups of units in battle. Commands with authority and tactical precision.

templates.name: Warfare Architect
templates.description: A strategic mastermind specialized in overseeing and coordinating ground forces. Expert in battlefield control and multi-squad operations.

templates.name: Exo-Colonel
templates.description: An experienced leader skilled at commanding squads in the heat of battle. Excels at frontline tactics and swift decision-making.

templates.name: Tactician
templates.description: A novice leader trained for ground operations and urban warfare. Efficient in deploying small units and securing tactical objectives.

templates.name: Shieldmaster
templates.description: The ultimate protector, commanding advanced shielding technology. Unyielding in defense and strategic positioning.

templates.name: Titan Guard
templates.description: A towering defender equipped with superior armor and kinetic barriers. Masters of endurance and area control.

templates.name: Bastion Defender
templates.description: An elite protector with advanced armor and tactical knowledge. Excels at safeguarding key objectives.

templates.name: Bulwark Specialist
templates.description: A defense expert specialized in fortified positions and heavy shielding. Known for absorbing and redirecting enemy assaults.

templates.name: Sentinel Veteran
templates.description: A seasoned guardian with reinforced armor and defensive techniques. Adept at holding lines under pressure.

templates.name: Sentinel Recruit
templates.description: An aspiring defender trained in protective tactics and shield-based combat. Reliable in securing positions.

templates.name: Warhound
templates.description: The ultimate raider, feared for brutal assaults and relentless aggression. Masters of high-risk, high-reward tactics.

templates.name: Strike Operative
templates.description: An elite raider specializing in surgical strikes and enemy disruption. Unmatched in ambush and assault operations.

templates.name: Enforcer
templates.description: A frontline attacker skilled in suppression and shock tactics. Ideal for breaking enemy formations.

templates.name: Gunslinger
templates.description: An expert marksman specialized in dual-wielding firearms and rapid engagements. Lethal at close to mid-range.

templates.name: Scout Veteran
templates.description: A seasoned scout with enhanced precision and speed. Effective in hit-and-run tactics.

templates.name: Scout Recruit
templates.description: A novice raider trained for swift attacks and reconnaissance missions. Skilled in infiltration and mobility.

templates.name: Warfare Elite
templates.description: A top-tier warrior with unmatched proficiency in both offensive strikes and defensive resilience. The ultimate battlefield asset.

templates.name: Warfare Specialist
templates.description: An elite combatant proficient in coordinating assaults and defensive holds. Expert in tactical versatility.

templates.name: Battleforged Veteran
templates.description: A hardened veteran with extensive combat experience. Masters a wide range of weapons and defensive maneuvers.

templates.name: Field Operative
templates.description: A specialized fighter adept at both reconnaissance and frontline engagements. Excels in adapting to unpredictable battlefields.

templates.name: Trooper Veteran
templates.description: A battle-tested soldier with improved combat skills and defensive tactics. Reliable in diverse combat scenarios.

templates.name: Trooper Recruit
templates.description: A versatile recruit trained for both offense and defense. Skilled in basic weapons and tactical adaptability.

templates.name: Void Walker
templates.description: A conscious dark energy entity manifesting as an ethereal quadruped. It phases through walls, absorbs incoming attacks, and generates micro-portals to bypass physical barriers. Its ever-shifting form harbors a miniature cosmos, with galaxies and stars swirling within its ephemeral silhouette. Only those who’ve glimpsed beyond reality’s veil can earn the attention of such a being.

templates.name: Chronowyrm
templates.description: A mini time dragon hatched from an egg found in a dimensional rift. His ability to briefly slow time around him allows him to dodge deadly attacks. His scales change color depending on the era he "feels" and he can sometimes predict near future events. Extremely rare and difficult to tame.

templates.name: Nebulon
templates.description: A genetically modified flying feline, the result of abandoned military experiments. Its membranous wings and reinforced alloy claws allow it to attack in flight and carry its master short distances. Its changing coat provides camouflage in various environments.

templates.name: Luminyx
templates.description: A semi-sentient bioluminescent mushroom that attaches itself to its owner's shoulder via small symbiotic roots. Its glow varies depending on surrounding dangers and it can absorb certain toxins to protect its host. Its spores can temporarily blind enemies or illuminate dark areas. It pulses to the rhythm of its companion's emotions.

templates.name: DogX403 - The "Hotdog"
templates.description: This canine species is the result of a cross between a Earth dog embryo and a Ma-Boar. With its heat-resistant fur and superior intelligence, this dog is excellent for protection and searching for objects. Affectionately nicknamed "Hotdog" by its creators.

templates.name: Ma-Boar
templates.description: Domesticated with cybernetic implants, with blackish fur and slightly luminescent eyes, he is the ideal companion for seasoned mercenaries. It can detect resources and warn its master of dangers. Be careful, it may explode if stressed too much.

templates.name: Ma-Boar
templates.description: Domesticated with cybernetic implants, with blackish fur and slightly luminescent eyes, he is the ideal companion for seasoned mercenaries. It can detect resources and warn its master of dangers. Be careful, it may explode if stressed too much.

templates.name: Fragment
templates.description: A remnant of forgotten power, drawn from the ashes of sacrifice. Its force reshapes the fate of the worthy.

templates.name: Exalted Antimatter
templates.description: Exalted Antimatter is a perfectly spherical manifestation of pure energy, pulsating with a controlled yet immense power. Its flawless form radiates an ethereal glow, subtly bending space around its dark core.

templates.name: Concentrated Antimatter
templates.description: Concentrated Antimatter is a dense, highly compressed core of pure energy, suspended in a delicate balance between creation and annihilation. Its intense, fluctuating glow distorts its surroundings, radiating an overwhelming presence.

templates.name: Volatile Antimatter
templates.description: Volatile Antimatter is an unstable, high-energy substance that flickers between existence and annihilation, radiating a chaotic glow. Its ever-shifting form pulses with raw, unpredictable energy, distorting the space around it.

templates.name: Eternal Chromium Prism
templates.description: The Eternal Chrome Prism is a refined metal with an unchanging, mirror-like surface that refracts light in infinite, changing patterns. Its impeccable structure gives it an almost timeless presence, as if suspended beyond the flow of time.

templates.name: Dimensional Chromium Prism
templates.description: The Dimensional Chrome Prism is a metallic hexagon with a reflective surface that distorts light into fascinating multi-dimensional patterns. Its complex structure appears to move subtly, creating an illusion of depth beyond its physical form.

templates.name: Radial Chromium Prism
templates.description: Radial Chromium Prism is a hexagonal metallic liquid prism with a highly reflective, chrome-like surface that radiates shifting spectral hues. Its structured form enhances its geometric symmetry, creating a striking interplay of light and depth.

templates.name: Perfected Singularity
templates.description: Perfected Singularity is an impeccably stabilized gravitational core, appearing as a smooth, obsidian-like void with an unwavering presence. Its flawless structure bends light seamlessly around it, creating an illusion of infinite depth and absolute stillness.

templates.name: Concentrated Singularity
templates.description: Concentrated Singularity is a densely compressed core of immense gravitational energy, appearing as a dark, shimmering void. Its compact form distorts light and matter around it, giving it an intense, almost infinite depth.

templates.name: Unstable Singularity
templates.description: Unstable Singularity is a dense, shifting mass that warps its surroundings with an unpredictable gravitational pull. Its ever-changing form flickers between states of matter, radiating an eerie, fluctuating energy.

templates.name: Absolute Etherium Liquid
templates.description: Absolute Etherium Liquid is a perfectly stabilized, radiant fluid with an unparalleled level of purity and cohesion. Its ethereal glow and seamless flow give it an almost surreal, otherworldly presence.

templates.name: Purified Etherium Liquid
templates.description: Purified Etherium Liquid is a crystal-clear, luminescent fluid with an impeccably refined molecular structure. Its smooth, ever-flowing form emits a soft glow, reflecting its unmatched purity.

templates.name: Compressed Etherium Liquid
templates.description: Compressed Etherium Liquid is a dense, translucent substance with a shifting, fluid-like consistency despite its high compression. Its surface shimmers with an ever-changing interplay of light, giving it an almost ethereal appearance.

templates.name: Infinite Neon Core
templates.description: Infinite Neon Core is a radiant material with a seemingly boundless internal luminosity, exhibiting a dynamic interplay of light and energy. Its structure gives it a glow that appears to extend beyond its physical boundaries.

templates.name: Ultra-Pure Neon Core
templates.description: Ultra-Pure Neon Core is a spherical crystalline material with an immaculate atomic structure, emitting a vibrant, ethereal glow. Its chaotic composition enhances its refractive brilliance.

templates.name: Concentrated Neon Core
templates.description: Concentrated Neon Core is a cubic material with a dense, luminous structure, radiating a subtle neon glow. Its compact atomic arrangement gives it a strikingly uniform shape and exceptional stability.

templates.name: Structured Oreon
templates.description: Structured Oreon is a golden metal with a precisely arranged crystalline framework, enhancing its stability and strength. Its organized atomic composition gives it a distinctive balance between rigidity and adaptability.

templates.name: Condensed Oreon
templates.description: Condensed Oreon is a dense, golden metal with a tightly packed atomic structure, giving it remarkable solidity and resilience. Its lustrous surface and high mass-to-volume ratio make it distinct from other metallic compounds.

templates.name: Flexible Oreon
templates.description: Flexible Oreon is a golden-hued semi-liquid metal with an adaptive molecular structure, allowing it to shift between fluid and solid states. Its unique composition gives it a smooth, metallic luster and exceptional malleability.

templates.name: Reinforced Synthetic Carbon
templates.description: Reinforced Synthetic Carbon is a high-strength material engineered with optimized bonding structures for enhanced mechanical performance. Its advanced composition improves resistance to stress, heat, and environmental factors.

templates.name: Modified Synthetic Carbon
templates.description: Modified Synthetic Carbon is an engineered material with enhanced structural properties, offering superior durability and thermal stability. Its unique composition results from advanced processing techniques that optimize its molecular arrangement.

templates.name: Raw Synthetic Carbon
templates.description: Raw synthetic carbon is an unrefined composite of carbon chains, forming a dense, spherical matrix. Its dark, matte surface absorbs light.

templates.name: Perfected Quantum Crystal
templates.description: Perfected Quantum Crystal is a flawlessly harmonized lattice that resonates with an almost imperceptible hum. Its surface refracts light in mesmerizing patterns, appearing both solid and intangible at the same time.

templates.name: Enhanced Quantum Crystal
templates.description: Enhanced Quantum Crystal is a stabilized yet dynamic lattice that radiates a soft, pulsating luminescence. Its structure subtly bends light around it, creating the illusion of shifting depth and dimension.

templates.name: Fragile Quantum Crystal
templates.description: Fragile Quantum Crystal is a delicately structured lattice that shimmers with an ethereal, ever-shifting glow. Its translucent form appears to flicker between states, as if caught between different realities.

templates.name: Purified Nano-Metal
templates.description: Purified Nano-Metal is an advanced alloy with a perfectly harmonized nanostructure, eliminating impurities at the atomic level. Its surface displays a finely textured, almost organic pattern, subtly shifting under different lighting conditions.

templates.name: Stabilized Nano-Metal
templates.description: Stabilized Nano-Metal features a meticulously engineered, honeycomb-like structure at the microscopic level. Its surface scatters light in complex patterns, giving it a distinct, matte metallic sheen with a subtle inner glow.

templates.name: Primary Nano-Metal
templates.description: Primary Nano-Metal is a meticulously structured alloy composed of self-arranging nanoscopic lattices. Its surface shimmers with a subtle metallic sheen, adapting seamlessly to shifts in pressure and temperature.

templates.name: Exalted Plasmo-Fibers
templates.description: Exalted Plasmo-Fibers are a rare, high-energy weave that hums with a vibrant, otherworldly radiance. Their intricate lattice seems to pulse with raw power, shifting in color as if alive.

templates.name: Reinforced Plasmo-Fibers
templates.description: Reinforced Plasmo-Fibers are a dense, interlaced material infused with stabilized plasma currents. Their structure shimmers with a deep, pulsating glow, radiating an intense yet controlled energy.

templates.name: Raw Plasmo-Fibers
templates.description: Raw Plasmo-Fibers are an unrefined, plasma-infused filament with a complex, interwoven structure. Their unique composition gives them a dynamic, ever-shifting glow and an almost weightless feel.

templates.name: Quantum Key NTT
templates.description: A Quantum Key NTT opening any Quantum Chest. Be careful, it disintegrates after use.

templates.name: 500K Coins
templates.description: 500,000 coins to spend in the Planetary Defense Bot Shop. You may not need it, but it looks nice in the wallet. Burn it to credit your Discord game account.

templates.name: 50K Coins
templates.description: 50,000 coins to spend in the Planetary Defense Bot Shop. Find your next cutting-edge equipments. Burn it to credit your Discord game account.

templates.name: 5K Coins
templates.description: 5,000 coins to spend in the Planetary Defense Bot Shop. Enough to buy an unreasonable quantity of RedBoars... or mint a Quantum Chest. Burn it to credit your Discord game account.

templates.name: Quantum Key
templates.description: A Quantum Key opening any Quantum Chest. Be careful, it disintegrates after use.

templates.name: Quantum Chest
templates.description: A Quantum Chest containing the entire universe, but only one thing can be collected at a time.
